Popular business mogul, Obinna Iyiegbu aka Obi Cubana, has expressed excitement over the note containing affirmation of love from his wife, Ebele Iyiegbu aka Lusheby. The nightlife boss revealed he woke up Wednesday morning to a lovely piece from his better half, reassuring him of not just her unending love for total committment throughout their lifetime. According to Cubana via his Instagram page, “Woke up over here to this lovely note from my beautiful wife @lush_eby.” The note reads: “Dear Obinna, I write this note this morning to remind you of my commitment to love you even on your weakest days and strongest days.   Chioma Ifemeludike mocks colleagues denying alleged affairs…     Show your face, Apostle Suleman dares blogger over s3xual…     £4,269 raised as Eedris Abdulkareem undergoes kidney surgery   “I’m going to love you in your happy moments and your sad moments. “I’m going to always be your shoulder to lean on. I’m going to love you UNCONDITIONALLY just as Christ loves me because He is the one that models Love for me. “Through thick and thin, till death do us part, I’m going to be by your side to make sure you fulfill every destiny that God has given you. “Be assured of my support all through this journey of life. “Gold and Silver have I none, but what I do have, I give unto thee.” NEVER FORGET THIS. Good morning Sunshine.”